{"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"relationshipsSections":[{"type":"conformsTo","title":"Conforms To","kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem"},{"type":"text","text":" proposes layouts to add in your views some checkboxes components with labels and icons."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"If you want to use a checkbox with only an indicator prefer instead "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem"},"kind":"symbol","topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem\/init(isOn:labelText:helperText:icon:isInversed:isError:isReadOnly:hasDivider:)"],"anchor":"Initializers","generated":true,"title":"Initializers"},{"generated":true,"title":"Instance Properties","anchor":"Instance-Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem\/body"]},{"generated":true,"title":"Default Implementations","anchor":"Default-Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem\/View-Implementations"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","kind":"attribute","text":"MainActor"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSCheckboxItem"}]}]},{"content":[{"anchor":"Layouts","type":"heading","text":"Layouts","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The component can be rendered as two different layouts:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": the component has a leading indicator, a label and optional helper texts, and an optional trailing decorative icon"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"inverse","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": like the "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" layout but with a trailing checkbox indicator and a leading optional image","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Indicator states","anchor":"Indicator-states"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The checkbox indicator has three available states:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"selected"}]},{"text":": the checkbox is filled with a tick, the user has made the action to select the checkbox","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"unselected","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": the checkbox is empty, does not contain a tick, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the checkbox"}]}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you are looking for a checkbox component with three states, use instead "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Particular-cases","text":"Particular cases"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"A dedicated look and feel is implemented for that if the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isError"},{"type":"text","text":" flag is risen."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"In addition, the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem"},{"text":" can be in read only mode, i.e. the user cannot interact with the component yet but this component must not be considered","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"as disabled."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","text":"Accessibility considerations"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}]},{"type":"text","text":" will use several elements to describe the component: if component disabled \/ read only, if error context, the label and helper texts and a custom checkbox trait."}]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Forbidden by design","anchor":"Forbidden-by-design"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a read only component."}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component."}]},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both a read only and a disabled component."}]}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Code samples","anchor":"Code-samples","level":2},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an unselected checkbox","    @Published var isOn: Bool = false","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $isOn, labelText: \"Hello world\")","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label, but in read only mode (user cannot interact yet, but not disabled).","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $isOn, labelText: \"Hello world\", isReadOnly: true)","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label, and an helper text.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $isOn, labelText: \"Bazinga!\", helperText: \"Doll-Dagga Buzz-Buzz Ziggety-Zag\")","","    \/\/ A trailing checkbox with a label, an helper text and an icon.","    \/\/ The inverse layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $isOn,","                     labelText: \"We live in a fabled world\",","                     helperText: \"Of dreaming boys and wide-eyed girls\",","                     isInversed: true,","                     icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"))","","    \/\/ A trailing checkbox with a label, an helper text, an icon, a divider and is about an error.","    \/\/ The inverse layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $isOn,","                     labelText: \"Rescue from this world!\",","                     helperText: \"Put your hand in mine\",","                     icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"),","                     isInversed: true,","                     isError: true,","                     divider: true)","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label, but disabled.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $isOn, labelText: \"Hello world\")","        .disabled(true)","","    \/\/ Never disable a read only or an error-related checkbox as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $isOn, labelText: \"Hello world\", isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $isOn, labelText: \"Hello world\", isReadyOnly: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Design-documentation","text":"Design documentation"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"See "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/23f1c1-checkbox"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.12.0"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"Since","style":"note","type":"aside"}],"kind":"content"}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"OUDSComponents"}],"symbolKind":"struct","title":"OUDSCheckboxItem","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSCheckboxItem"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents16OUDSCheckboxItemV","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSCheckboxItem"}],"roleHeading":"Structure"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudscheckboxitem"]}],"references":{"doc://ouds-ios.OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The catalog of all components provided by OUDS. It contains also "},{"code":"View","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" extensions and "},{"code":"ViewModifiers","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" to apply tokens and styles on components and higher-level views.","type":"text"}],"title":"OUDSComponents","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents","identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents","type":"topic"},"doc://ouds-ios.OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponent